headline: Northern Trust Asset Management Appoints Chief Investment Strategists
summary: CHICAGO & LONDON, May 28, 2025--Northern Trust Asset Management, a leading global investment management firm with US$1.3 trillion in assets under management as of March 31, 2025, has appointed Gary Paulin as chief investment strategist, International and Joseph Tanious as chief investment strategist, North America.
